text:
Did you use any Hubl in it? If you worked locally and are using a formatting tool like prettier or something like that it can sometimes format the hubl in an odd way. That formatting wont always show up as an error on here but will kill the compilation process.

I have found that using the “show output” toggle has been really helpful in finding these errors.
I am using HubL, but not using a formatter.  I've also looked through the output and don't see anything weird.
